---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/layout/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="OpenClaw Config Generator (Roadmap) + Secure Config Checklist | CoClaw"
  description="Visual config generator is in development. Use this secure checklist and links to official docs to create a safe OpenClaw configuration today."
  keywords="OpenClaw config generator, OpenClaw configuration, openclaw.json, OpenClaw allowlist, OpenClaw security"
>
  <Section containerClass="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Visual Config Generator</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-default-800 dark:text-default-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      The no-code OpenClaw configuration generator is under development. In the meantime, use the
      secure checklist below and the official docs to build your configuration safely.
    </p>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-divider bg-content1 p-6 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Secure Config Checklist</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-3 text-default-800 dark:text-default-600">
        <li>
          Locate your config file (commonly <code>~/.openclaw/openclaw.json</code> after onboarding).
        </li>
        <li>
          Set a conservative DM policy for messaging channels (start with an <strong
            >allowlist</strong
          >).
        </li>
        <li>Restrict who can control the agent: add your number/user IDs to the allowlist.</li>
        <li>Keep tools locked down: only allowlist the tools you actually need for that agent.</li>
        <li>
          Test changes in a non-production environment before enabling on your primary account.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
      <a
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-6 py-3 font-semibold"
        href="https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        OpenClaw on GitHub
      </a>
      <a
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-divider bg-content1 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-foreground"
        href="https://docs.openclaw.ai"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Official Docs
      </a>
      <a
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-divider bg-content1 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-foreground"
        href="/getting-started"
      >
        Getting Started
      </a>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
